title: Luigi Dinielli
text:
Luigi Dinielli (born 6 October 1996) is an Italian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="S.S.%20Fidelis%20Andria%201928">Fidelis Andria</a>.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Serie%20C">Serie C</a> debut for <a href="Foggia%20Calcio">Foggia</a> on 29 December 2016 in a game against <a href="Siracusa%20Calcio%20%282013%20club%29">Siracusa</a>.
